serviceRequestRequesterNameSearchParameter

Parameter requester.name:string

Searches for serviceRequest based on the Practitioner's full or partial name eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/ServiceRequest?requester:Practitioner.name={name}

ResourceServiceRequest
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesServiceRequest
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
